
// This Hyperlambda code snippet uses the [signal] slot to invoke the [magic.ai.massage] slot. It loads content from a file using [io.file.load], retrieves the file name from [.arguments], and specifies the type from [.arguments]. The slots involved are: [signal] to invoke a slot, [magic.ai.massage] to process AI-related tasks, [io.file.load] to load file content, and [.arguments] to access input parameters.
signal:magic.ai.massage
   content:x:@io.file.load
   prompt:x:@.arguments/*/file/*/name
   type:x:@.arguments/*/type
